OL,3,CStabbing victim would have called
OL,4,Cmurderer one of 'best friends'
OL,6,FA killer has been jailed for life
OL,7,Fafter pleading guilty to the murder of
OL,8,Fa man in Newcastle.
OL,10,FGavin Train fatally stabbed Bradley
OL,11,FTams on Cartmel Green, in Slatyford,
OL,12,Fjust before midnight on 6 December
OL,13,Flast year
OL,15,FResponding to a report of an assault,
OL,16,Fofficers found Bradley, 23, with
OL,17,Fserious injuries and he died at the
OL,18,Fscene.
