OL,3,CStabbing victim would have called
OL,4,Cmurderer one of 'best friends'
OL,6,FCCTV showed Train, along with his
OL,7,Fmother Andrea Train and friend Lewis
OL,8,FAllison, fleeing the area following
OL,9,Fthe attack.
OL,11,FAn investigation revealed that Train
OL,12,Fsought retribution for a previous
OL,13,Fdispute, and was notified that Bradley
OL,14,Fwas in the area that night.
OL,16,FNorthumbria Police said the 24-year-
OL,17,Fold followed Bradley's taxi in a car,
OL,18,Fbefore confronting him and engaging in
OL,19,Fa verbal and physical altercation.
