OL,3,CStabbing victim would have called
OL,4,Cmurderer one of 'best friends'
OL,6,FBradley suffered a single wound to his
OL,7,Fside and escaped into a neighbouring
OL,8,Fblock of flats, but died a short time
OL,9,Flater despite the efforts of emergency
OL,10,Fresponders.
OL,12,FTrain, of Rothay Place, Newcastle, was
OL,13,Farrested within hours and charged with
OL,14,Fmurder. He pleaded guilty to the
OL,15,Foffence at Newcastle Crown Court in a
OL,16,Fhearing last month.
OL,18,FOn Monday (22 July), he attended the
OL,19,Fsame court where he was sentenced to
OL,20,Flife imprisonment, and must serve a
OL,21,Fminimum of 21 years.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/12
