OL,3,CStabbing victim would have called
OL,4,Cmurderer one of 'best friends'
OL,6,FAllison, 24, of Roundhill Avenue,
OL,7,FBlakelaw, and Andrea Train, 49, of
OL,8,FRothay Place, Newcastle, both pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty to charges of violent disorder
OL,10,Fin the same hearing last month.
OL,12,FAndrea Train was sentenced to three
OL,13,Fyears and four months behind bars,
OL,14,Fwith half of the term to be served on
OL,15,Flicence.
OL,17,FAllison was handed the same sentence,
OL,18,Fand ordered to serve a further six
OL,19,Fmonths in custody for a separate
OL,20,Foffence of breaching a community order.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/12
