OL,4,Cmurderer one of 'best friends'
OL,6,FSpeaking after the sentencing,
OL,7,FBradley's sister Lauren Weatherson
OL,8,Fdescribed the family's heartbreak at
OL,9,Flosing their loved one at the hands of
OL,10,Fthose he would have classed as his
OL,11,F"best friends".
OL,13,F"Bradley was the closest thing I had
OL,14,Fleft of my father," she said. "My
OL,15,Fbrother and I grew up side by side
OL,16,Fhaving only 14 months between us. He
OL,17,Flit up every room he stepped in, he
OL,18,Fwas always so full of life.
