OL,3,CStabbing victim would have called
OL,4,Cmurderer one of 'best friends'
OL,6,F"My nights have become sleepless, my
OL,7,Fdays have become tiresome. I am
OL,8,Fconstantly thinking about my brother's
OL,9,Flast moments in life and the pain he
OL,10,Fwould have felt physically and
OL,11,Femotionally.
OL,13,F"Any homicide would be difficult to
OL,14,Fget past but the people responsible in
OL,15,Fmy brother's case makes this a whole
OL,16,Flot worse. My brother was killed by
OL,17,Fpeople he would have called his best
OL,18,Ffriends.
OL,20,F"I am not the same person anymore, no
OL,21,Fone in my family is. We are all broken.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU|D@AOU
