OL,3,CStabbing victim would have called
OL,4,Cmurderer one of 'best friends'
OL,6,F"One thing I wish for in the future is
OL,7,Ffor these people to think about their
OL,8,Factions so that another family doesn't
OL,9,Fhave to go through the pain and grief
OL,10,Fmy family and I have."
OL,12,FBradley's mother Julie Weatherson,
OL,13,Falso paid tribute to her son and spoke
OL,14,Fof her pain at losing a child.
OL,16,FShe said: "My life changed forever
OL,17,Fwhen Bradley was born. I cannot
OL,18,Fdescribe the love I felt when he was
OL,19,Ffirst placed into my arms.
