OL,4,Cmurderer one of 'best friends'
OL,6,F"From a young age, Bradley was full of
OL,7,Fcharacter and always had lots of
OL,8,Ffriends. I would describe Bradley as
OL,9,Fthe life and soul of the party and
OL,10,Falways the joker.
OL,12,F"He loved and adored his family and
OL,13,Fwould do anything for us.
OL,15,F"Since Bradley was taken from me, my
OL,16,Flife has not been the same. I am not
OL,17,Fthe same person ` a part of me died
OL,18,Fwhen Bradley died."
