OL,6,FShe added: "Bradley wasn't a saint and
OL,7,Fdid have his own issues prior to his
OL,8,Fdeath but I always knew how much he
OL,9,Floved and cared for me.
OL,11,F"People say that time is a healer, but
OL,12,FI am yet to experience this. I miss my
OL,13,Fhandsome boy every second of every
OL,14,Fday."
