OL,6,FLeading the investigation, Detective
OL,7,FChief Inspector Katie Smith, of
OL,8,FNorthumbria Police, said: "This has
OL,9,Fbeen an incredibly tragic case and my
OL,10,Fthoughts remain with Bradley's family
OL,11,Fand friends during what has been a
OL,12,Fdevastating time for them.
OL,14,F"No sentence will erase the heartbreak
OL,15,Fof losing a beloved son, brother and
OL,16,Ffather."
